timing_report_..._rise_fall_map(25.10)  timing_report_..._rise_fall_map(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_lead_trail_to_rise_fall_map

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_lead_trail_to_rise_fall_map

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting  of rise/fall edge times, instead of lead/trail edge
       times of a clock (that are reported using the report_clocks command).

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

